{"tid":1781062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動］15/12（日）英領集會","createTime":"2019-12-13T01:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T02:22:08.000Z","uid":2099,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0eb0b78c106cafb73d8b95ff48c87140093c80","tid":1781062,"uid":2099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T01:33:49.000Z","msg":"⚠️英領緊急再聚集⚠️<br />\n🇬🇧 授權英國新國會 🇬🇧<br />\n‼️ 終止中英聯合聲明 ‼️<br />\n<br />\n我地邀請所有手足集結英領<br />\n正式要求新國會因中共違約而終止中英聯合聲明🔥<br />\n已有多位「下議員」候選議員答應若當選會向國會表達我地嘅訴求，但英國同我地好需要爭取更多支持！<br />\n<br />\n流程:<br />\n1)剖析多份法律文件，分析終止聲明嘅合法性同正當性<br />\n2)香港獨立黨背景交代+連登常見誤解<br />\n3)公佈英領留守手足未來去向<br />\n4)Q&amp;A<br />\n<br />\n祝幾位答應協助我地嘅下議院議員成功當選，結果會於香港時間12月13日(今日)公佈，若成功當選，集會將變得「更有意義」，請留意channel最新消息<br />\n<br />\n日期: 2019年12月14日 (六)⚠️<br />\n時間: 20:00-22:00<br />\n地點: 英國駐香港總領事館<br />\n自備:英國旗、英聯邦旗、#香港旗<br />\n頻道:@ukterminatejd<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uipjtta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUipjtta.jpg&h=a7ed99c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EnXtmOb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEnXtmOb.jpg&h=a7c112f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MUZoaGw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMUZoaGw.jpg&h=807bfe8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce2ca1986fb1eba23a00f31bf413671d9a7c3d1e","tid":1781062,"uid":16607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93dea77cd7bd0a1749885dcf9cc7ba301262730","tid":1781062,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:08:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0b69e7ac3cb2095f6e7912ff7f4e602df1625b3","tid":1781062,"uid":2099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:22:08.000Z","msg":"14號 星期六 先岩<br />\n15號 出去行街啦！ <br />\n<br />\nsorry 出錯左 <br />\n多謝大家click入黎"}]}